(put sd card in main machine to paste access token thing)


TRY CRON




put timer/service files in ~/.config/systemd/user/
reboot
test service with:
	systemctl --user start boardpdf.service
start timer with:
	systemctl --user start boardpdf.timer
make it permanent with:
	systemctl --user enable boardpdf.timer




github instead of dropbox?

git clone https://github.com/gav989/boardpdf
extract boardpdf/scripts.zip to pwd
run all to create boardpdf.zip
copy boardpdf.zip into boardpdf
cd into boardpdf
git add src
git commit -m "uploading new files"
git push origin master

